# 4. Buat values khusus ingress untuk chart broapp

Maintenant on ne expose  plus avec `LoadBalancer`.  
On change le strategie:

```text
service.type = ClusterIP
ingress.enabled = true
ingress.className = nginx
```

Créer fichier:

```bash
cat > values-ingress.yaml <<EOF
service:
  type: ClusterIP
  port: 80

ingress:
  enabled: true
  className: nginx
  annotations:
    nginx.ingress.kubernetes.io/ssl-redirect: "false"
  hosts:
    - host: ${HOST}
      paths:
        - path: /
          pathType: Prefix
  tls: []
EOF
```

On regarde:

```bash
cat values-ingress.yaml
```

